Halleluya!

0:03:37.600,0:03:40.120
Kwa hivyo, tunaweza kuelewa wapi dada yetu anatokea.

0:03:40.120,0:03:43.020
Alikuwa na tatizo la VVU / UKIMWI 1.

0:03:43.020,0:03:48.480
Tunataka uweke msisitizo jinsi shida hii imeathiri maisha yako.

